								<span class="image main"><img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" /></span>
								<p>Researching and prototyping new technologies is a passion of mine. Over the past 5 years I have watched technology as a whole, and the blockchain space specifically, evolve at an amazing rate. Below are some of the projects, articles and design documents I worked on as part of the technical strategy work I have done.</p>
