								<li><a href="https://github.com/johnwhitton/blockchain-eval/blob/master/substrate.md" target="_blank">Jincubator - Layer 1 protocol technology comparison</a></li>
								<p></p>
								<p>For prototyping please checkout <a href="https://johnwhitton.dev/docs/" target="_blank">the playground</a> to see some of the API, SDK and development tools I have created.</p>
								<p>Finally for newer work please follow me on <a href="https://medium.com/@john_whitton" target="_blank">medium @john_whitton</a></p>
